    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Page.Title">目录位置</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Page.Description">配置 Skyweaver 的会话、配置、调试和会话流文件保存位置。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Page.Hint">目录设置会立即写入默认 Configuration 目录中的 Directories.xml。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.ChatSessions.Label">聊天会话目录</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.ChatSessions.Hint">设定聊天会话 ChatSessions 保存的位置。默认在用户文件夹/Skyweaver/ChatSessions 之下。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.ConfigurationFiles.Label">配置文件目录</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.ConfigurationFiles.Hint">设定配置文件 Configuration 保存的位置。Directories.xml 始终保留在用户文件夹/Skyweaver/Configuration 中。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Debug.Label">调试文件目录</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Debug.Hint">设定调试目录 Debug 保存的位置。默认在用户文件夹/Skyweaver/Debug 之下。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.SessionFlows.Label">会话流目录</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.SessionFlows.Hint">设定会话流节点图保存的位置。默认在用户文件夹/Skyweaver/Nodegraphs 之下。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.AerialCity.Label">AerialCity 目录</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.AerialCity.Hint">设定 AerialCity RAG 数据库与映射文件保存的位置。默认在用户文件夹/Skyweaver/AerialCity 之下。</system:String>
