    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.MaxCompaction.Hint">上下文窗口达到上限且 MinCompaction 无法工作时，使用全量的压缩方法压缩会话上下文。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.LifeCycle.Content">启用 LifeCycle</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.LifeCycle.Hint">特定工具调用结果将获得生命周期限制。在一定会话轮数后，这些工具调用结果会在上下文中被自动失效落盘。代理可以取回这些工具调用结果。一旦取回，LifeCycle 对此失效。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.LifeCycleRatio.Label">LifeCycle 比率</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.LifeCycleRatio.Hint">调整 LifeCycle 实际运作时的生命周期长度。结果向上取整。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.RnnOptimization.Label">RNN 优化</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.RnnOptimization.Content">启用循环神经网络优化的压缩</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.RnnOptimization.Hint">仅限于 RWKV、Manba 等 RNN 语言模型启用。如果启用，上下文限制会被移除，更重要的结果和内容会被移动到更新的位置，以保证它们时刻对线性注意力产生更大影响。需开启外推以获得无限上下文。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Status.MinCompactionSaved">MinCompaction 设置已保存。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Status.MaxCompactionSaved">MaxCompaction 设置已保存。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Status.LifeCycleSaved">LifeCycle 设置已保存。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Status.LifeCycleRatioSaved">LifeCycle 比率已保存。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Status.RnnOptimizationSaved">循环神经网络优化压缩设置已保存。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Instruction.1">1. 此页设置会立即写入当前配置文件目录中的 ContextManagement.xml。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ContextCompression.Instruction.2">2. 除 MinCompaction 外，当前选项只负责持久化配置，运行时行为尚未接入。</system:String>

    <system:String x:Key="Memory.Page.Title">记忆</system:String>
