    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.ProjectId.Label">项目 ID (ProjectId)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.ProjectId.Hint">托管搜索数据存储的 Google Cloud 项目 ID。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.Location.Label">区域位置 (Location)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.Location.Hint">Vertex AI Search 的区域位置，例如 'global'、'us' 或 'eu'。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.DataStoreId.Label">数据存储 ID (DataStoreId)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.DataStoreId.Hint">Vertex AI Search 中用于索引关联的数据存储标识符。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.CredentialsJson.Label">凭证 JSON (CredentialsJson)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.CredentialsJson.Hint">Google Cloud 服务账号凭证的 JSON 内容或其文件的绝对路径。留空将使用应用默认凭证 (ADC)。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.ApiKey.Label">API 密钥 (ApiKey, 备用)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.ApiKey.Hint">备用的 API 密钥。如果未提供服务账号凭证，则可用 API 密钥进行简单检索鉴权。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.MaxResults.Label">最大结果数 (MaxResults)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.MaxResults.Hint">每次检索从数据存储中获取的最大文档条数。</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.SearchModel.Label">数据源类型 (SearchModel)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Search.Vertex.SearchModel.Hint">指定关联数据存储的底层模式（'unstructured' 代表网页/纯文本，'structured' 代表结构化数据）。</system:String>
